oc:kn_1017233b a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:Procedure ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When responding to data subject requests" ;
    oc:directiveContent "1. Gather all personal data of the requester across systems 2. Apply exemptions and document basis 3. Prepare response (fulfill or explain denial) 4. If denying, cite specific legal basis 5. Inform requester of complaint right 6. Document response and retain records" ;
    oc:stepOrder 2 .

oc:kn_2e575240 a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When assessing response timeline compliance" ;
    oc:directiveContent "GDPR breach notification: 72 hours to supervisory authority. CCPA acknowledgment: 10 business days. GDPR data subject response: 30 days (+60 extension). CCPA substantive response: 45 days (+45 extension). LGPD response: 15 days." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Missing regulatory deadlines can result in fines and enforcement actions" .

oc:kn_486eb080 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:Procedure ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When handling data subject requests" ;
    oc:directiveContent "1. Identify request type (access, rectification, erasure, portability, restriction, objection, opt-out) 2. Identify applicable regulations by jurisdiction 3. Verify requester identity with proportionate measures 4. Log the request with date, type, identity, regulation, deadline, handler" ;
    oc:stepOrder 1 .

oc:kn_50839870 a oc:DesignPrinciple,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When generating compliance check output" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Structure output as: Summary (proceed/proceed with conditions/requires review) → Applicable Regulations table → Requirements table (Met/Not Met/Unknown) → Risk Areas → Recommended Actions → Approvals Needed → Further Review" ;
    oc:hasRationale "Structured output enables decision-makers to quickly assess status and take action" .

oc:kn_5674e61b a oc:AntiPattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When generating the Summary section of the output" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Never provide a blanket 'proceed' assessment without identifying the specific regulations that apply and the jurisdiction involved." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Oversimplified approvals create false confidence and liability exposure" .

oc:kn_783e77f8 a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When reviewing Data Processing Agreements" ;
    oc:directiveContent "When reviewing DPAs, focus on: sub-processor notification rights, breach notification within 24-48 hours, audit rights, data deletion timelines (30-90 days), specified processing locations, and current EU SCCs (2021 version)." ;
    oc:hasRationale "These are the most commonly negotiated and risk-bearing DPA provisions" .

oc:kn_8692ebf1 a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "Always, when presenting any compliance check output" ;
    oc:directiveContent "This skill assists with legal workflows but does NOT provide legal advice. All compliance assessments must be reviewed by qualified legal professionals." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Regulatory requirements change frequently and non-lawyer AI assessments carry liability risk without professional review" ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

oc:kn_a35e2118 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:KnownIssue ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When referencing specific regulations, timelines, or thresholds" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Regulatory requirements change frequently; the skill's regulatory knowledge may be outdated. Always verify current requirements with authoritative sources." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Privacy laws are actively evolving globally (e.g., new US state laws, EU AI Act) and static references become stale" ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_cb7d50ed a oc:AssumptionBoundary,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When the user expects organization-specific compliance answers" ;
    oc:directiveContent "The skill assumes knowledge of major privacy frameworks (GDPR, CCPA/CPRA, LGPD, POPIA, PIPEDA, PDPA, Privacy Act Australia, PIPL, UK GDPR) but cannot know organization-specific policies, existing agreements, or internal approval workflows." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Compliance is context-dependent; the skill provides framework-level analysis, not organization-specific legal opinions" .

oc:kn_e047672d a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When gathering information from the user before analysis" ;
    oc:directiveContent "The three most important inputs for a compliance check are: (1) specificity of the action, (2) geographic jurisdiction, and (3) what personal data is involved. These drive most compliance requirements." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Compliance obligations are jurisdiction-specific and data-type-dependent; vague inputs produce unreliable assessments" .

